org.drools.lang.descr
Class DescrFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.drools.lang.descr.DescrFactory

public class DescrFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This is the factory for ALL descriptors (eventually). This will be tied in a with a package builder session, so it can add in context information for validation when parsing.
